Some kind of bogus cloth simulation.


Make and Install:
   cabal install cabal-dev

   git clone https://github.com/dan-t/Gamgine
   git clone https://github.com/dan-t/clothsim

   cd clothsim
   cabal-dev add-source ../Gamgine
   cabal-dev install


Usage:
   clothsim


Control:
   Pick the cloth by holding the left mouse button pressed
